<h1>Congratulations!</h1>
<p>Your publishing request for the following has been approved.</p>
<p>Title: <%= @title %></p>
<p>Record ID: <%= @record_id %></p>
<p>Record Type: <%= @name_of_pub_type %></p>
<p>Publishing ID: <%= @publishing_id %></p>
